    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanus</persName> divina providentia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> petitioni dilecti sui clementer favet.
                        Notum sit omnibus sancte et catholice Ecclesie filiis me, quem ad hoc divina
                        gratia promovit in principem ut ecclesiarum defensor atque ditator existam,
                        ob salutem et redemptionem anime <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei et <persName key="#parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3003">Fredesinde</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">matris</rs> mee et ob meorum peccatorum indulgentiam,
                        dedisse, concessisse et confirmasse <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                        </orgName>confessoris Christi sito in <placeName ref="#places/109">Monte
                            Casino</placeName> et domino <persName key="#Abbots #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/2421">Desiderio</persName> eiusdem monasterii <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>, per <rs key="#Intercessory">interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Principissa #marriage" ref="#people/3011"
                            >Gaytelgrimme</persName>
                        <rs key="#Principissa">principisse</rs>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxoris</rs> mee, <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3061">Sancte Agathe</orgName> constructam prope
                            <rs key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs>, cum <rs key="#Curtes">curtibus</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >villanis</rs> et cum universis suis pertinentiis, quas princeps
                        Richardus pater meus ibi dedit, et qualiter <persName key="#Chaplain"
                            ref="#people/4213">Gualterius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chaplain">capellanus</rs> eam tenuit, cum omnibus suis
                        pertinentiis in die obitus suis, ad possessionem, potestatem et dominationem
                        predicti monasterii Sancti Benedicti et domni abbatis suorumque successorum,
                        remota omni contrarietate et molestatione mortalium. Quod siquis, diabolica
                        suasione compulsus, hanc nostram dationem, oblationem, concessionem violare
                        irritasve facere temptaverit, <rs key="#Penalty">centum auri optimi
                            libras</rs> persolvat, medietate nostro Palatio et medetiatem prescripto
                        monasterio et predicto abbati suisque successoribus, et soluta pena hoc
                        scriptum firmum et inviolabile maneat in perpetuum et firmum credatur et
                        diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu mea subscripsi et mei sigilli
                        inpressione feci sigillare. Signum domni Iordani <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">IORDANVS</persName>. Per iussionem prefate
                        serenissime potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3005">Cansolinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> in anno principatus ipsius vicesimo octabo et
                        vicesimo tertio anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs>
                        eius <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Gaiete</geogName></placeName>. Data octabo kalendas Martii, anno ab
                        incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi M octoagesimo quinto. Scriptum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per nonam
                        indictionem.</ab>
